by lyrixx at 2020-02-21T14:19:49Z

@GromNaN Usually we prefer to use the `{{ include }}` syntax over `{% include %}`:
It's more semantic, `{{ }}` print something where `{% %}` should not (yes, initial implem was an error)

Anyway, I already dreamed about the ES2015 syntaxt in twig. I would be awesome to have the support everywhere

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by GromNaN at 2020-02-21T14:21:13Z

Thanks for the recommendation @lyrixx. I've updated the description.

