by yoriiis at 2020-05-20T10:31:43Z

Hi, is there any way this will eventually be merged or is this a dead option?

The current syntax has several duplicates when passing parameters, as in the example below.

```twig
{{ include 'template.html.twig' with {
    isCustomGrid: isCustomGrid,
    orderedPeriod: orderedPeriod,
    route: route,
    routeParams: routeParams
} only }}
```

The previous request dates from 2013 but the developers and languages have evolved a lot since.

The changes from @GromNaN make it easier to write the above example.

```twig
{{ include 'template.html.twig' with {
    isCustomGrid,
    orderedPeriod,
    route,
    routeParams
} only }}
```
